{"tid":1559465,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係時候為運動正名喇","createTime":"2019-09-10T23:33:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T23:53:58.000Z","uid":269265,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6e8e55a3517512f62e54cad12f581d739b2fcc49","tid":1559465,"uid":269265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T23:33:04.000Z","msg":"連國歌都有，但我哋仲係叫緊呢場運動做「呢場運動」，太唔掂啦。<br />\n<br />\n而家列出幾個比較多人提嘅名，大家再集思廣益。<br />\n<br />\n1 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Water revolution</span></span> (但中文名莫衷一是，比較多人譯做 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">流水革命</span></span>）<br />\n<br />\n2 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">時代革命</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n3 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n4 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">榮光革命</span></span> (配合《願榮光歸香港》，英文可以譯返做 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Glorious Revolution of Hong Kong</span></span>?)<br />\n<br />\n注意：個名最好可以同時配合返「運動」兩個字，<br />\n例如當年嘅雨傘運動/雨傘革命，方便傳媒使用。<br />\n<br />\n大家投個票？或者仲有乜建議？"},{"pid":"a696c92d8082983e8a20b2eb1a0fb956b1cada5b","tid":1559465,"uid":202464,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T23:34:54.000Z","msg":"唔係不嬲叫開反送中咩？"},{"pid":"3822a69e0e4269cd37033d9d0afe3ea13e76bf4d","tid":1559465,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a696c92d8082983e8a20b2eb1a0fb956b1cada5b","tid":1559465,"uid":202464,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T23:34:54.000Z","msg":"唔係不嬲叫開反送中咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T23:36:22.000Z","msg":"反歸終 唔係起點咋咩"},{"pid":"c4663699348591582ee48b8d5595a03b54844578","tid":1559465,"uid":58068,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T23:36:47.000Z","msg":"革命係 個運動完左先會定命<br />\n孫中山都唔係講：我地宜家搞緊辛亥革命啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4de81b54da4143ce2418e6eecbefbb7f84ae3133","tid":1559465,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T23:37:15.000Z","msg":"2 Times Revolution<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce0012ca3022cd1b05a44ec655cd5843c6306cb4","tid":1559465,"uid":269265,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c4663699348591582ee48b8d5595a03b54844578","tid":1559465,"uid":58068,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T23:36:47.000Z","msg":"革命係 個運動完左先會定命<br />\n孫中山都唔係講：我地宜家搞緊辛亥革命啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T23:53:58.000Z","msg":"史學上，其實同意㗎，辛亥革命的確係1911年發生咗先有呢個名。<br />\n<br />\n但而家有個困難，就係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">話語權問題</span></span>。傳媒同坊間仲係叫緊做 「反送中運動」或者「反修例運動」，咁佢哋一句「送中條例已經撤回」，就好易一口否定呢場運動。我哋要令公眾明白，呢場運動一早已經超出反送中嘅目標。<br />\n<br />\n而且有個清晰嘅名，亦方便外國傳媒報導，因為有啲外國人真係以為撤咗等於贏咗。"}]}